text: Jumaya stadium Club de Fútbol Calamocha is a Spanish football team based in Calamocha, in the autonomous community of Aragon. Founded in 1940 it plays in Tercera División, Group 17, holding home games at Jumaya. ==History== The club was founded in 1940 and has always moved into regional categories of Aragon, especially the Primera Regional and in recent times the Regional Preferente. In the 2017–18 season he achieved for the first time in his history the promotion to national categories of Spanish football and is framed in the Tercera División, Group 17. ==Season to season== {|
